OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772089483
OL,3,C'Discrimination, violence and unlawful
OL,4,Cactions': Should we fear humanoid
OL,5,Crobots?
OL,7,FWords by Akshay Raja
OL,9,FFrom the growing use of large language
OL,10,Fmodels (LLMs) such as ChatGPT, to
OL,11,Fplans for the launch of driverless
OL,12,Ftaxis in the UK this year, we are
OL,13,Fwitnessing the transformative effects
OL,14,Fof artificial intelligence (AI) in our
OL,15,Fday-to-day lives.
OL,17,FOne technology yet to make its way
OL,18,Finto everyday use is the humanoid
OL,19,Frobot. But this could soon change.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772089483
OL,3,C'Discrimination, violence and unlawful
OL,4,Cactions': Should we fear humanoid
OL,5,Crobots?
OL,7,FVideos emerging from China's Spring
OL,8,FFestival Gala showed humanoids
OL,9,Fperforming fluid martial arts moves in
OL,10,Fperfect synchronicity.
OL,12,FA video released by Chinese robotics
OL,13,Fcompany Unitree shows humanoid robots
OL,14,Fdemonstrating their kung fu moves at
OL,15,FBeijing's Temple of Heaven. Credit:
OL,16,FCCTV
OL,18,FAs these humanlike figures flipped,
OL,19,Fleapt and kicked with ease, you would
OL,20,Fbe forgiven for thinking they have
OL,21,Fbeen doing it for years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772089483
OL,3,C'Discrimination, violence and unlawful
OL,4,Cactions': Should we fear humanoid
OL,5,Crobots?
OL,7,FBut footage from less than 12 months
OL,8,Fearlier showed similar robots
OL,9,Fstumbling around on a football pitch,
OL,10,Ftripping up over nothing and waddling
OL,11,Finto each other.
OL,13,FSome experts remain sceptical. They
OL,14,Fwarn against being disillusioned by
OL,15,Fthese performative displays,
OL,16,Fhighlighting instead the security and
OL,17,Fsafety risks humanoid robots could
OL,18,Fpose if we do not exercise caution.
OL,20,FSo should we be excited by this
OL,21,Ftechnology, or worried?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772089483
OL,3,C'Discrimination, violence and unlawful
OL,4,Cactions': Should we fear humanoid
OL,5,Crobots?
OL,7,FPhysical harms and safety risks
OL,9,FDr Andrew Hundt is a Computing
OL,10,FInnovation Fellow at Carnegie Mellon
OL,11,FUniversity. He distinguishes between
OL,12,Fthe pre-scripted displays of humanoids
OL,13,Fand how they would perform in new,
OL,14,Funpredictable locations.
OL,16,FDr Hundt highlights the limitations of
OL,17,Fthe technology's current capacities,
OL,18,Fsaying: "If they then have to, say,
OL,19,Finteract in crowds or manipulate
OL,20,Fobjects (...) suddenly their abilities
OL,21,Fappear to drop."
OL,26,@|D@Ipm|D@Mpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772089483
OL,3,C'Discrimination, violence and unlawful
OL,4,Cactions': Should we fear humanoid
OL,5,Crobots?
OL,7,FRobotics manufacturer, Humanoid,
OL,8,Fechoes Dr Hundt's claim. In an email
OL,9,Fto ITV News, the company writes: "If
OL,10,Fthere's one thing that the industry is
OL,11,Fdoing wrong at the moment, it is the
OL,12,Fhype."
OL,14,FWhile the team at Humanoid recognise
OL,15,Fthe impressive nature of the
OL,16,Fdemonstrations, they clarify these
OL,17,F"are mostly here for marketing reasons
OL,18,Fand don't necessarily reflect real
OL,19,Fcommercial readiness."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772089483
OL,3,C'Discrimination, violence and unlawful
OL,4,Cactions': Should we fear humanoid
OL,5,Crobots?
OL,7,FAndrew Hundt explains the dangers
OL,8,Fhumanoids pose, despite the impressive
OL,9,Fdevelopments we have seen over the
OL,10,Flast year.
OL,12,F"There is a lot of potential to help
OL,13,Fpeople out and save people a lot of
OL,14,Ftrouble," Dr Hundt says. "But on the
OL,15,Fother hand, these systems are getting
OL,16,Fcapable enough to look like they can
OL,17,Fwork, but still dangerous enough to be
OL,18,Fa risk to people."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772089483
OL,3,C'Discrimination, violence and unlawful
OL,4,Cactions': Should we fear humanoid
OL,5,Crobots?
OL,7,FClarifying how dangerous robots can
OL,8,Factually be, he suggests AI systems
OL,9,Fare significantly limited in handling
OL,10,Finteractive safety, saying "they're
OL,11,Fjust really not good at long-term
OL,12,Freasoning at the moment." Dr Hundt
OL,13,Ffears there could be "a number of
OL,14,Fscandals on the way" if this is not
OL,15,Fresolved.
OL,17,FHe does not believe enough is
OL,18,Fcurrently being done to deal with
OL,19,Fthese issues, but developers at
OL,20,FHumanoid say safety is their main
OL,21,Ffocus.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772089483
OL,3,C'Discrimination, violence and unlawful
OL,4,Cactions': Should we fear humanoid
OL,5,Crobots?
OL,7,FThe company is currently working on
OL,8,Ftwo models for commercial and
OL,9,Findustrial use. These will only be
OL,10,Fintroduced to homes once Humanoid have
OL,11,Fensured "robots can operate in human
OL,12,Fenvironments".
OL,14,FFactory floors offer a suitable
OL,15,Fenvironment to trial this due to their
OL,16,Fstructured and predictable
OL,17,Fenvironments, which allow the company
OL,18,F"to test robots, collect data, and
OL,19,Fdevelop reliable capabilities before
OL,20,Fmoving into more complex environments
OL,21,Flike homes".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772089483
OL,3,C'Discrimination, violence and unlawful
OL,4,Cactions': Should we fear humanoid
OL,5,Crobots?
OL,7,FDiscrimination
OL,9,FAnother issue encountered by Dr Hundt
OL,10,Fduring his research is that the AI
OL,11,Fmodels, which are intended for use in
OL,12,Fthe humanoid robots, "tend to also do
OL,13,Fcertain kinds of harm based on
OL,14,Fdifferences in race, gender, and
OL,15,Fdisability status."
OL,17,FOne AI system suggested a robot should
OL,18,Fdisplay a "face of disgust" if facing
OL,19,Fa Christian, Muslim or Jewish person.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772089483
OL,3,C'Discrimination, violence and unlawful
OL,4,Cactions': Should we fear humanoid
OL,5,Crobots?
OL,7,FSome humanoids have already exhibited
OL,8,Fsigns of discriminatory treatment
OL,9,Fbased on race and ethnicity.
OL,11,FDr Masoumeh Mansouri is an Associate
OL,12,FProfessor in the School of Computer
OL,13,FScience at the University of
OL,14,FBirmingham. She similarly points to
OL,15,Ffindings that LLM-driven robots risk
OL,16,F"enacting discrimination, violence,
OL,17,Fand unlawful actions."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772089483
OL,3,C'Discrimination, violence and unlawful
OL,4,Cactions': Should we fear humanoid
OL,5,Crobots?
OL,7,FIf similar AI models are run in the
OL,8,Fsort of humanoid robots we have seen
OL,9,Frecently, Dr Mansouri fears how bad
OL,10,Fthe consequences could be.
OL,12,FDevelopers at Humanoid said their
OL,13,Fresponsibility is "to address bias
OL,14,Frisks in AI systems".
OL,16,FPrivacy issues
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772089483
OL,3,C'Discrimination, violence and unlawful
OL,4,Cactions': Should we fear humanoid
OL,5,Crobots?
OL,7,FPrivacy issues are not unique to
OL,8,Fhumanoids and robotics, but Dr
OL,9,FMansouri recognises we are entering a
OL,10,F"new territory" where robots are
OL,11,Fgranted wider access to private and
OL,12,Fpublic spaces.
OL,14,FGiven the lack of care with which
OL,15,Ftechnology is typically introduced to
OL,16,Fthe public domain, Dr Mansouri fears
OL,17,Fthere could be particularly harmful
OL,18,Fconsequences.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772089483
OL,3,C'Discrimination, violence and unlawful
OL,4,Cactions': Should we fear humanoid
OL,5,Crobots?
OL,7,FShe has observed two LLMs which could
OL,8,Fbe used in humanoids approving
OL,9,Frequests to take non-consensual
OL,10,Fphotographs of someone in a shower.
OL,12,FDr Masoumeh Mansouri explains the
OL,13,Fpotential for humanoids to violate
OL,14,Fpersonal privacy if deployed on a
OL,15,Fwider scale.
OL,17,FFor the team at Humanoid, "robots will
OL,18,Fonly become widespread if people trust
OL,19,Fthem". A key pillar of this trust is
OL,20,F"data privacy you can control".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772089483
OL,3,C'Discrimination, violence and unlawful
OL,4,Cactions': Should we fear humanoid
OL,5,Crobots?
OL,7,FAs well as having a responsibility to
OL,8,Fensure the safety of the technology
OL,9,Fwhich is implemented, Humanoid
OL,10,Fbelieves developers "need to educate
OL,11,Findustries and the public on how these
OL,12,Fplatforms work and how to use them
OL,13,Fsafely".
OL,15,FShould we be worried about humanoids?
OL,17,FNeither Dr Hundt or Dr Mansouri
OL,18,Fbelieve humanoid robots are currently
OL,19,Fsafe enough to be deployed in the
OL,20,Fpublic domain.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30715
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772089483
OL,3,C'Discrimination, violence and unlawful
OL,4,Cactions': Should we fear humanoid
OL,5,Crobots?
OL,7,FFor Dr Hundt, though, the risks should
OL,8,Fnot be overstated. He believes the
OL,9,Fharms posed can be managed through the
OL,10,Fregulation of the AI systems which
OL,11,Fthey are driven by.
OL,13,FHe says: "I do think that people
OL,14,Fshould be worried about it, not in an
OL,15,Fexistential sense, but more in a sense
OL,16,Fthat you should also be worried about
OL,17,Fcars when you cross the street because
OL,18,Fcars are extremely dangerous
OL,19,Fgenerally."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30716
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772089483
OL,3,C'Discrimination, violence and unlawful
OL,4,Cactions': Should we fear humanoid
OL,5,Crobots?
OL,7,FFor Humanoid, the technology should
OL,8,Fnot be feared as something that will
OL,9,Freplace humans, but rather be seen as
OL,10,Fa tool "to amplify human potential".
OL,12,FDespite recognising the technology
OL,13,Fwill not develop overnight, the
OL,14,Fcompany does not think we are far away
OL,15,Fas many think. Humanoid says: "One of
OL,16,Fthe biggest misconceptions about the
OL,17,Findustry is that humanoids are still
OL,18,Fdecades away.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30717
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772089483
OL,3,C'Discrimination, violence and unlawful
OL,4,Cactions': Should we fear humanoid
OL,5,Crobots?
OL,7,F"But in reality, development is moving
OL,8,Fextremely fast. Many companies
OL,9,Fglobally are already running pilots in
OL,10,Fwarehouses, logistics centres, retail,
OL,11,Fand manufacturing.
OL,13,F"The first limited home-use pilots
OL,14,Fhave also begun in some countries.
OL,15,FWithin a few years, it's very likely
OL,16,Fpeople will personally know someone
OL,17,Finteracting with a humanoid robot."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30718
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772089483
OL,3,C'Discrimination, violence and unlawful
OL,4,Cactions': Should we fear humanoid
OL,5,Crobots?
OL,7,F"As AI capabilities improve, robots
OL,8,Fwill increasingly handle repetitive,
OL,9,Fmonotonous, or hazardous work, and
OL,10,Fthese are tasks that are difficult to
OL,11,Ffill or that are unsafe for humans",
OL,12,Fthe company says. This will enable
OL,13,Fpeople to pursue more "creative" or
OL,14,F"meaningful" roles, it says.
OL,16,FAnd it looks like we will not have
OL,17,Flong to wait to find out whether
OL,18,Fhumanoids will be helping with the
OL,19,Fadmin - or impacting our lives in more
OL,20,Fharmful ways.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
